<plot>Soviet followup to several Hollywood aviation films of the 1930s.3 Russian test pilots risk their lives making a round-the-world, non-stop flight on "Pobeda-1" ["Victory-1"]. Their experimental craft loses radio contact and is alleged by Japanese ( "fascist") radio to have crashed fatally. But hero Klim's mother and brother Sasha never give up hope, and Sasha launches a desperate air search, hoping to find the missing "Pobeda' without loss of life.....</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?436553</url></doc>
